reviewText: Never thought I see this again
the skysurfers are cool  my son has all the volumes  but the series is incomplete  some episodes are missing I hope the complete series will come soon to dvd

The Thin Case The Used DVD Came In Was Slightly Damaged And Didn't Have The Artwork Cover, But That's OK; Just As Long As The DVD Works.  And It Does!  I Would Like To Get All The Episodes Of This Series.  Hopefully They'll ALL Be On DVD Soon.
